Class DeleteExpression

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
IExpression
public class DeleteExpression
extends ExpressionImpl

Special implementation of ExpressionImpl representing a delete-expression.

The grammar production rule of the expression is: delete-expression ::= DELETE [CASCADE] <value-expression> [ WHERE boolean-expression ]

Author:
Sven Krosse
